<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Content Admin</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050505;
      --surface: #101010;
      --surface-strong: #171717;
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --text: #f3f3f3;
      --text-muted: #9d9d9d;
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --gold-soft: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.14);
      --danger: #ff8c75;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.16), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #090909 0%, #030303 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
    }

    .panel {
      width: min(100%, 440px);
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015)),
        var(--surface);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .error {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 117, 0.2);
      background: rgba(255, 140, 117, 0.08);
      color: var(--danger);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .actions {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .primary-link,
    .secondary-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      font: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .primary-link {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d6b35b, #b99032);
      color: #111;
      border: none;
    }

    .secondary-link {
      background: var(--surface-strong);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .primary-link:hover,
    .secondary-link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .secondary-link:hover {
      border-color: var(--gold);
    }

    .note {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Royal Drive</p>
    <h1>Content Admin</h1>
    <p>Open the CMS to edit site copy, media, locations, FAQs, and footer content directly from the Git-backed content file.</p>

    <div class="actions">
      <a class="primary-link" href="/admin/">Open CMS</a>
      <a class="secondary-link" href="/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Live Site</a>
    </div>

    <p class="note">If this is your first time signing in, the CMS will prompt you through the Netlify Identity login flow before opening the editor.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
